        <div class="mb-track-block">
          <div class="mb-track-label">PATENT CLAIM</div>
          <div class="mb-track-text">A resident inference model that learns the mechanical signature of a specific physical printer — feed tension, roller wear, ink viscosity drift — and intervenes <em>before</em> the jam occurs. Not jam recovery. Pre-failure prediction. One model per device. Trained on that printer's history, not a generic fleet average.</div>
